{
  "id": "64cf20a6795f14001b3d9a3d",
  "title": "決定したとアナウンスしたことをすぐ覆す",
  "created": 1691295913,
  "updated": 1691390845,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "64cf20a6795f14001b3d9a3d",
      "text": "決定したとアナウンスしたことをすぐ覆す",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1691295913,
      "updated": 1691295913
    },
    {
      "id": "64cf316a5e90c000007aa90b",
      "text": "　[朝令暮改]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1691300202,
      "updated": 1691300211
    },
    {
      "id": "64cf20aa5e90c00000fe2e5e",
      "text": " 　しかし[過ちては改むるに憚ること勿れ]",
      "userId": "60508ed36a7abc00235e90c0",
      "created": 1691295913,
      "updated": 1691300218
    },
    {
      "id": "64cf20ab5e90c00000fe2e5f",
      "text": "　[二転三転]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691295914,
      "updated": 1691326549
    },
    {
      "id": "64cf9853e600350000389e2c",
      "text": "　[朝三暮四]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1691326548,
      "updated": 1691357935
    },
    {
      "id": "64d08168e5172d0000cb8162",
      "text": "　[前言撤回]",
      "userId": "5c30ba88e98efe0017e5172d",
      "created": 1691386214,
      "updated": 1691386217
    },
    {
      "id": "64d012e85b98c20000b861ec",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1691357929,
      "updated": 1691357929
    },
    {
      "id": "64d0924ced60e600008775f0",
      "text": "判断を誤ったことに気づいたときにすぐに直したと考えると、良いこと",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1691390541,
      "updated": 1691390732
    },
    {
      "id": "64d0926fed60e600008775f2",
      "text": "指示内容が変わって混乱を巻き起こすと考えると、良くないこと",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1691390577,
      "updated": 1691390735
    },
    {
      "id": "64d0924ced60e600008775f1",
      "text": "\tこれを防ぐには意思決定に関わる者全員が疑問や反対を持たなくなるまで議論を尽くすのが良い[ろほぬもめぽよ.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1691390541,
      "updated": 1691390747
    },
    {
      "id": "64d0931bed60e600008775f4",
      "text": "\t\t理想論では？",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1691390748,
      "updated": 1691390762
    },
    {
      "id": "64d0933ced60e600008775f5",
      "text": "\t\tこれを効率的に実現するには意思決定に関わるもの全員が疑問点や反対意見を隠さずに即座にその場で言う必要がある",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1691390782,
      "updated": 1691390835
    },
    {
      "id": "64d09373ed60e600008775f6",
      "text": "\t\t\t隠しておくと議論が長引くため",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1691390836,
      "updated": 1691390845
    },
    {
      "id": "64d092aeed60e600008775f3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1691390640,
      "updated": 1691390640
    },
    {
      "id": "64cf98cfe6003500001f7616",
      "text": "cf. [自分が発言した言葉に縛られる]",
      "userId": "62a91a7a083437001de60035",
      "created": 1691326673,
      "updated": 1691326676
    },
    {
      "id": "64cf98d0e6003500001f7617",
